---
import BaseHead from '../../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../../../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`論文 - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="研究出版物和工作論文" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<article>
				<h1>論文</h1>

				<section>
					<h2>已發表文章</h2>

					<div class="publication-entry">
						<h3>Can the Energy Transition Be Smooth? A General Equilibrium Approach to the EROEI</h3>
						<p class="authors">Fagnart, J.-F.; Germain, M.; Peeters, B.</p>
						<p class="journal">Sustainability, 2020, 12, 1176</p>
						<p class="description">
							使用一般均衡框架分析能源轉型挑戰，
							重點關注能源投資回報率（EROEI）動態。
						</p>
						<p class="links">
							<a href="https://doi.org/10.3390/su12031176" target="_blank">DOI: 10.3390/su12031176</a>
						</p>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>工作論文（審查中）</h2>

					<div class="publication-entry">
						<h3>Cyclical Pattern in International Financial Flows to the Semi-periphery</h3>
						<p class="authors">Peeters, B.</p>
						<p class="status">審查中</p>
						<p class="description">
							檢視流向半邊陲國家的國際金融流動的週期性模式，
							分析國際收支危機的結構性動態。
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="publication-entry">
						<h3>Monetary policy response or economic integration: what drives international monetary policy spillovers?</h3>
						<p class="authors">Peeters, B.; Girard, A.; Gnabo, J.-Y.</p>
						<p class="status">審查中</p>
						<p class="description">
							探討貨幣政策反應與經濟一體化在解釋國際貨幣政策溢出效應中的相對重要性。
						</p>
						<p class="note">包含論文PDF、數據集和R代碼</p>
					</div>

					<div class="publication-entry">
						<h3>Medium-Term Cycles and Financial Crises in Semi-periphery Countries</h3>
						<p class="authors">Peeters, B.; Defraigne, J.-C.</p>
						<p class="status">審查中</p>
						<p class="description">
							分析半邊陲經濟體的中期經濟週期及其與金融危機的關係，
							探討結構性脆弱性。
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="publication-entry">
						<h3>How has Financial Globalization impacted Monetary Policy? An overview</h3>
						<p class="authors">Peeters, B.</p>
						<p class="status">修訂中</p>
						<p class="description">
							全面概述金融全球化對貨幣政策執行、有效性和傳導機制在不同經濟背景下的影響。
						</p>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>進行中的工作</h2>

					<div class="publication-entry">
						<h3>Instability in the IMS: The Role of Inflation Spillovers among Advanced Economies</h3>
						<p class="authors">Peeters, B.</p>
						<p class="status">進行中</p>
					</div>

					<div class="publication-entry">
						<h3>Integrating Intangible Assets into the World-System Approach</h3>
						<p class="authors">Peeters, B.</p>
						<p class="status">進行中</p>
					</div>

					<div class="publication-entry">
						<h3>The Debt-Trap Diplomacy of China and Western Countries</h3>
						<p class="authors">Peeters, B.; Sauvenier, M.; Seynaeve, C.</p>
						<p class="status">進行中</p>
					</div>

					<div class="publication-entry">
						<h3>The Underestimated Functions of Tax Havens</h3>
						<p class="authors">Peeters, B.</p>
						<p class="status">進行中</p>
					</div>

					<div class="publication-entry">
						<h3>Industrialization and Natural Disasters</h3>
						<p class="authors">Peeters, B.</p>
						<p class="status">進行中</p>
					</div>
				</section>
			</article>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	article {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	section {
		margin: 3rem 0;
	}

	.publication-entry {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
		background-color: var(--card-bg);
		border-radius: 4px;
		transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
	}

	.publication-entry:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(45, 126, 63, 0.2);
	}

	.publication-entry h3 {
		margin-top: 0;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--accent-dark);
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		line-height: 1.4;
	}

	.authors {
		font-style: italic;
		color: var(--text-color);
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.journal {
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--accent);
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.status {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
		background-color: var(--accent-light);
		color: white;
		border-radius: 12px;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
	}

	.description {
		margin: 1rem 0;
		line-height: 1.6;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.links {
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.links a {
		display: inline-block;
		margin-right: 1rem;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		background-color: var(--accent);
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 4px;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
	}

	.links a:hover {
		background-color: var(--accent-dark);
	}

	.note {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--accent);
		font-style: italic;
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.publication-entry {
			padding: 1rem;
		}

		.publication-entry h3 {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
		}
	}
</style>
